                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Baltimore</placeName>\n                <date>June 22</date>,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I addressed you a letter on <date>Monday</date> Last,<lb/> you can\n                confer a favor me, by writing me a few lines on <date>Sunday</date><lb/> next, &amp;\n                let me know if you received it, and why you have not answered<lb/> it, I saw Cousin\n                    <persName>David</persName> This morning, he begins to look like<lb/> himself\n                again, he says he is willing to do what he can,<lb/> we have very Hot weather here\n                now, times remarkably dull</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">I am</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">with much respect Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">your most obedient humble Servant</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">R Judah</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>my ink is so bad that can </p>\n            <p>scarcely write, please write on <date>Sunday</date></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p36h4d97x/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
